urch. Blessings, where they occur, are often at the discretion of the diocese, and the Church is nothing if not a devolved institution.     Share                   ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
